WEBVTT

00:00.022 --> 00:01.819
Previosly on "When Calls The Heart"

00:01.845 --> 00:03.748
It's not wrong to give
someone a second chance

00:03.773 --> 00:05.922
or to believe in the
power of redemption.

00:05.947 --> 00:08.134
I am crediting you with time served

00:08.159 --> 00:10.113
and granting you immediate parole.

00:10.138 --> 00:11.984
We secured the northern territories.

00:12.017 --> 00:13.390
I heard the reports.

00:13.415 --> 00:15.401
I know the mounties lost a
lot of good men up there.

00:15.426 --> 00:17.570
Abigail, the bank is going under.

00:17.595 --> 00:19.529
You're the mayor, what're
you going to do about this?

00:19.554 --> 00:22.456
One investor will take this
town in a bad direction

00:22.481 --> 00:23.616
and the other won't.

00:23.641 --> 00:25.166
The bank is reopening.

00:25.191 --> 00:26.555
Carson saved another life.

00:26.580 --> 00:27.523
Carson did it.

00:27.548 --> 00:28.583
We did it.

00:28.608 --> 00:30.311
I choose you and no other.

00:30.336 --> 00:31.438
With this ring...

00:31.463 --> 00:32.658
I thee wed.

00:34.477 --> 00:35.675
To the bride and the groom.

00:35.700 --> 00:36.266
Here, here.

00:36.291 --> 00:37.453
- To the bride and groom.
- Here, here.

00:37.478 --> 00:38.488
To married life.

00:38.521 --> 00:40.289
To being married to you.

00:40.322 --> 00:41.116
Are you saying...

00:41.141 --> 00:42.624
I'm ready to get back together.

00:42.658 --> 00:43.789
Why don't you come by
the office tomorrow

00:43.814 --> 00:46.270
and we'll see if we can't find
you some kind of promotion.

00:46.295 --> 00:47.663
Thank you, Lee, I appreciate that.

00:47.695 --> 00:49.564
I've been given an
assignment at Fort Clay.

00:49.597 --> 00:50.871
You're leaving again?

00:50.896 --> 00:53.833
When someone like Jack gives
so much of themselves,

00:53.858 --> 00:55.166
they're never really gone.

00:55.191 --> 00:58.018
Elizabeth, you're gonna have a baby.

